<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - Digital Garden</title>

</head>
<body>

    <div class="container mt-4 mb-4">
        <header class="mx-auto text-center d-flex flex-column align-items-center">
        <img src="~/images/plant.jpg" alt="plants in a row" class="img-fluid">

        <h1 class="fw-bold mt-4" style="font-size: 3rem;">Welcome to Digital Garden</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.2rem;">Track your plants, log their growth, and share tips with the community.</p>
        <a asp-controller="MyPlant" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-success btn-lg mt-3">View My Plants</a>
        </header>

        <section class="text-center my-5">
            <h2>What is a digital garden?</h2>
            <p class="lead">A simple way to orgize your plnts, keep track of their progress, and connect with fellow gardening enthusiasts.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="row text-center my-5">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h3>🌱 <a asp-controller="MyPlant" asp-action="Index" class="text-dark text-decoration-none hover:text-decoration-underline">Track Your Plants</a></h3>
                <p>Keep a record of watering schedules, sunlight exposure, and soil conditions to ensure your plants thrive.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h3>📖 <a asp-controller="CareLog" asp-action="Index" class="text-dark text-decoration-none hover:text-decoration-underline">Care Log</a></h3>
                <p>Document every step of your plant’s journey, from the first sprout to full bloom. Look back at your notes to learn what works best.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h3>🌍 <a asp-controller="CommunityTip" asp-action="Index" class="text-dark text-decoration-none hover:text-decoration-underline">Community Tips</a></h3>
                <p>Join a network of fellow plant lovers. Share insights, ask for advice, and discover new gardening techniques.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
